title: U.S. stocks end little changed
text:
U.S. stocks end little changed 10:03pm GMT - 01:12 
Wall Street gave up early gains after the Federal Reserve said it sees inflation rising this year, signaling it remains on track to boost interest rates again in March. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
